==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὕψιστος / hupsistos / hoop'-sis-tos

===Etymology===
*Superlative from the base of [[ὕψος]]; 

===Adjective===
'''ὕψιστος'''

# highest, that is, (masculine singular) the [[Supreme]] ([[God]]), or (neuter plural) the [[heavens]]: - most high, [[highest]].

